This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) category as it proposes a visual tracking method. The use of online metric learning suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The incorporation of feature dimensions and optimization problems suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) categories.
